Kernel IP routing table
Destination     Gateway         Genmask         Flags Metric Ref    Use Iface
default         _gateway        0.0.0.0         UG    100    0        0 enp0s1
192.168.64.0    0.0.0.0         255.255.255.0   U     100    0        0 enp0s1
